reviewText: Brand new worked with no problem and great shows.
Enjoy watching these fascinating creatures. Some hoaky stuff, but pretty good over all for us shark "fin-atics"!
Love it so entertaining I get stoned pop it in and bam in another world
Every week is Shark Week, and I love it.

ABSOLUTELY LOVE SHARK WEEK!!!!!
ONLY gave 1 Star...

Good variety with nice audio/video quality. Lots of content!
Got this dvd for my wife and she really love this series

One of my favorite Shark Week seasons! Loved the Megalodon special and also Submarine's. I think it's cool to mix a little fun and historical lore into educational programs. This was a great mix of specials so of course the whole set is a must-have for any SW fan.
And the count down to shark week begins with this!!!
The second disc came out of place, and was scratched is why this doesn't get 5 stars.
